{"tid":257603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]有冇人生過纖維瘤","createTime":"2017-05-25T11:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T13:37:09.000Z","uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a906a5e75186d90d1a6c8c4972757afe9a6b18d","tid":257603,"uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:48:46.000Z","msg":"利申:死肥仔<br />\nd幾個月個肚同腰都生左幾粒<br />\n左上腹都有，好細粒，醫生話係纖維瘤<br />\n有時會痛....不過醫生比左藥食就冇痛....但粒野仲係度<br />\n想問係咪一定要割?雖然唔痛但成日感覺到有粒野頂住<br />\n真心唔舒服<br />\n好驚會變惡性<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲生過?有咩好醫生介紹?"},{"pid":"cf002492d6bf7fba6833d6d641e8c3526a93d389","tid":257603,"uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"日日都好驚自己會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3d907280cc1c9db45d2ed00c1d1a64bcd93908","tid":257603,"uid":11843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:51:22.000Z","msg":"生過，平時high 到好q 痛<br />\n之後睇醫生話cut左佢好d<br />\n咁就切左"},{"pid":"687e85a933d89a3f95e5271ce8b70418d5d7623d","tid":257603,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:58:04.000Z","msg":"見過有人周身都有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 佢話唔痛"},{"pid":"89f18680ce2ee806459e463223a7ed208d275647","tid":257603,"uid":38426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生過，平時high 到好q 痛<br />\n之後睇醫生話cut左佢好d<br />\n咁就切左</blockquote><br />\n但我生左幾粒..切晒咪好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打睇邊個醫生?"},{"pid":"e6ec4b1c0413a30aeb0d4ad6c4a99db12344df47","tid":257603,"uid":18953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T12:03:09.000Z","msg":"生完切 切完又生<br />\n我排政府既"},{"pid":"f4384ece2a807dedb3